    <item>
      <title>BookLog</title>
      <link>https://faultypointer.github.io/notes/projects/booklog/booklog/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>faultypointer@proton.me (faultypointer)</author>
      <guid>https://faultypointer.github.io/notes/projects/booklog/booklog/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h3 id=&#34;introduction&#34; class=&#34;scroll-mt-8 group&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Introduction&#xA;  &#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;#introduction&#34;&#xA;        class=&#34;no-underline hidden opacity-50 hover:opacity-100 !text-inherit group-hover:inline-block&#34;&#xA;        aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to this heading&#34; tabindex=&#34;-1&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;svg&#xA;  xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;&#xA;  width=&#34;16&#34;&#xA;  height=&#34;16&#34;&#xA;  fill=&#34;none&#34;&#xA;  stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34;&#xA;  stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34;&#xA;  stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&#xA;  stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;  class=&#34;lucide lucide-link w-4 h-4 block&#34;&#xA;  viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path d=&#34;M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path d=&#34;M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71&#34; /&gt;&#xA;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;  &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A book reader and a journal.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;features-planned-not-final&#34; class=&#34;scroll-mt-8 group&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Features (planned not final)&#xA;  &#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;#features-planned-not-final&#34;&#xA;        class=&#34;no-underline hidden opacity-50 hover:opacity-100 !text-inherit group-hover:inline-block&#34;&#xA;        aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to this heading&#34; tabindex=&#34;-1&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;svg&#xA;  xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;&#xA;  width=&#34;16&#34;&#xA;  height=&#34;16&#34;&#xA;  fill=&#34;none&#34;&#xA;  stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34;&#xA;  stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34;&#xA;  stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&#xA;  stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;  class=&#34;lucide lucide-link w-4 h-4 block&#34;&#xA;  viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path d=&#34;M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path d=&#34;M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71&#34; /&gt;&#xA;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;  &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;read pdf, epub, mobi (decided to go with epub for prototype)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;simple ui with no ui clutter (mostly keyboard based)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;iced??&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;journals&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;write your thoughts like notes on any point of the book&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;write daily journals for the book&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;with initial thoughts (before reading) and final thoughts&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>BookLog Scratchpad</title>
      <link>https://faultypointer.github.io/notes/projects/booklog/scratchpad/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>faultypointer@proton.me (faultypointer)</author>
      <guid>https://faultypointer.github.io/notes/projects/booklog/scratchpad/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h3 id=&#34;how-to-read-epub&#34; class=&#34;scroll-mt-8 group&#34;&gt;&#xA;  How to read Epub&#xA;  &#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;#how-to-read-epub&#34;&#xA;        class=&#34;no-underline hidden opacity-50 hover:opacity-100 !text-inherit group-hover:inline-block&#34;&#xA;        aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to this heading&#34; tabindex=&#34;-1&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;svg&#xA;  xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;&#xA;  width=&#34;16&#34;&#xA;  height=&#34;16&#34;&#xA;  fill=&#34;none&#34;&#xA;  stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34;&#xA;  stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34;&#xA;  stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&#xA;  stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;  class=&#34;lucide lucide-link w-4 h-4 block&#34;&#xA;  viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path d=&#34;M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path d=&#34;M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71&#34; /&gt;&#xA;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;  &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;essentially&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;read the epub file (which is essentially a zip file)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;use zip::ZipArchive to extract all the files in the epub file&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;get the contents and their src from toc.rcx&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;read the files using src obtained from toc&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;strip all html tags to get the text only (tags and style maybe later)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;epub-structure&#34; class=&#34;scroll-mt-8 group&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Epub structure&#xA;  &#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;#epub-structure&#34;&#xA;        class=&#34;no-underline hidden opacity-50 hover:opacity-100 !text-inherit group-hover:inline-block&#34;&#xA;        aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to this heading&#34; tabindex=&#34;-1&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;svg&#xA;  xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;&#xA;  width=&#34;16&#34;&#xA;  height=&#34;16&#34;&#xA;  fill=&#34;none&#34;&#xA;  stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34;&#xA;  stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34;&#xA;  stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&#xA;  stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;  class=&#34;lucide lucide-link w-4 h-4 block&#34;&#xA;  viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path d=&#34;M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;path d=&#34;M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71&#34; /&gt;&#xA;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;  &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;what fields and methods the Epub structures should have. blatantly copied from &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/wustho/epr&#34;&gt;epr&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/aeosynth/bk&#34;&gt;bk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
